      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Matepoztli, tlen nochipa neci quence aniyoh huan ni tepoztli tlen xehxeltoc huan quitzacua tomaomiyo, nochipa nochihchihua ica ohomeh zo par tlen motzquitoc ica ce cadenah zo tepoztli cototzin.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
